p: A third Kenyan EO had ( E)-tagetone, dihydrotagetone, and alloocimene as its main components, but also contained sabinene, α-phellandrene, limonene, ( Z)-β-ocimene, ( E)-β-ocimene, ( Z)-tagetone, ( Z)-tagetenone, ( E)-tagetenone, elixene, silphiperfol-6-ene, ( E)-caryophyllene, α-humulene, and bicyclogermacrene [ 79].
